Interface HasCollisionController

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Ball, Circuit, Coil, ConductingSphericalShell, ConstantField, CurrentSlab, CylindricalMagnet, Dipole, ElectricDipole, EMObject, EMRadiator, FiniteWire, HollowCurrentShell, InclinedPlane, InfiniteConductingPlane, InfiniteLineCharge, InfiniteWire, LineMagneticDipole, MagneticDipole, PhysicalObject, PointCharge, PointChargeConductingSphere, RigidBar, RingOfCurrent, Seafloor, SlidingBox, Wall, WeightedPhysicalPendulum

    public interface HasCollisionController
    Provides methods for all objects implementing a collision controller.
